[B]Requirements[/B] (unchanged)

[LIST]
[*]Paper [B]1.21.1+[/B]
[*]Java [B]21+[/B]
[*]Not supported: Spigot, CraftBukkit, Folia
[/LIST]

[HR]

[B]Upgrade from v1.2.1[/B]

[LIST]
[*]Replace [B]ItemMagnet-1.2.2.jar[/B] in [CODE]plugins/[/CODE]
[*]Restart or [CODE]/itemmagnet reload[/CODE]
[*]Proximity lore stays [B]disabled[/B] until you enable it — existing servers are unaffected
[/LIST]

